'''The Nauglafring''' is the fourth chapter of ''[[The Book of Lost Tales Part Two]]''.

It narrates an early version of the [[Silmarillion]] chapter ''[[Of the Ruin of Doriath]]''. [[Nauglafring]] is an early name ([[Gnomish]]) of the item later known as [[Nauglamír]].

